ade sound?</span><hr size=1> Going to add my .02 to your templates, and since I am still learning the SB trade, take my input with a grain of salt.<br>
<br>
Template One<br>
Probably a good one to two hit template, the high axe ensures a nice solid one hit, CS at 34 allows for PA/CD combo. Stealth is a bit low for my tastes, though you can get the Realm Rank/Item combo to get you to 50, I'd recommend bumping it a bit higher in hopes of easing up on the amount of items needed. Envenom gets you a decent range of poison, alas no lifebane, but thats a personal pref. Left Axe is not worth mentioning in this template. Would recommend A nice 2 hander for opener, followed by a quick switch to left/right axes follow through allowing you to potentially hit your target with 3 venoms.<br>
<br>
Template Two<br>
Stealth, again I think is a tad low, but this is a personal pref, and depends on how you want to depend on items for stealth. CS at 25 seems odd, if your going for a hard opener this only gets you PA and a followup to Garrote. I'd consider maybe taking this higher for CD. Axe/LA 39, LA 39 only gets you a style that is follow up to an evade style, while Axe 39 gets you a positional, I'd consider stopping LA at Double Frost (34) I think and use the other points elsewhere. See comments above on your envenom.<br>
<br>
Template three<br>
<br>
Stealth, is a bit closer to a real spec for a lvl 50, you'd still be reliant on some stealth items against higher stealthers, but for most tasks you'd be pretty good, get RR3 and your at 40 which should be more than adequate. CS, you'd be simply MAD to try not to spec CS especially if your trying for the one shot. One shotters are typically high spec Main weapon/CS users, at least get PA (Spec 21) or CD Combo (34). Axe at 44 gets you a rarely used combo to an opening that requres a target to fumble, good luck there the only benefit is the bonus to weapon damage with the exta points. LA 44 gets you a nice combo followup to a rear positional besides the extra chance to hit. Again see inital comments on envenom.<br>
<br>
Two of the templates you spec'd are fairly common as far as design. Number one is a &quot;Critblade&quot; template relying on a hard opener to one shot an opponet maybe dropping a little poison on him just in case you didnt hurt him enough. Template two is a &quot;ShadowZerke&quot; type template relying on the high Melee keep you alive, and still swinging, since you use two weapons more often, you have a better chance of procing poison on an opponet. The final template is really a mess and I wouldn't even consider trying it as I feel personally that you'd be very unhappy with it, you'd never get the One Shot type hits, and though you could melee ok, if that's what your after you should go play a regular zerke, the only benefit is the envenom, and with it at that lvl, I dont think you'd last long enough in combat to drop your target with that type of venom unless you caught a loner or sniper.<br>
<br>
Anyway you play check out the character builder at catacombs. <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://daoc.catacombs.com/cbuilder.cfm">daoc.catacombs.com/cbuilder.cfm</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--> You can play with spec's and maybe find a happy medium, and remember you an Autotrain stealth to maybe get that exta point or two you'd need in your stealth.<br>
<br>
Good Luck<br>
<br>
Bargle <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showPrevMessage?topicID=2731.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showNextMessage?topicID=2731.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2731.topic&index=2><img src=http://www.thesafehouse.org/images/reply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.emailToFriend?topicID=2731.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.threadControl?topicID=2731.topic><img src=http://www.thesafehouse.org/images/dagger.jpg border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=2731.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=2731.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub35.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="thesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion">Main Lounge<option value="thesafehousecontractsbountiesjobsquestsetc">News Bulletin<option value="thesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies">Training Studio<option value="thesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers">The Back Alley<option value="thesafehousefrm13">Quests of Norra